Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think, I suppose she was around 11\Nwhen she became humanity's first Kamitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You stay young when you\Nturn into a Kamitsuki, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only on the outside.\NThe heart can also age, Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Renbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Renbokoji."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your godmother's name\Nis also Renbokoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just call her Godmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, when did you and\Nthe others receive the Blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, we called it a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gustav-eins.\NJIOR dropship located.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moderate damage to hull.\NNo sign of Valvraves or passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Repeating, moderate damage to hull.\NNo sign of Valvraves or passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At present, local army forces\Nare setting up a dragnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A thorough search is being conducted,\Nbut they have not been located yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with the Valvraves here. They're\Ntoo much for regional forces to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But sir, we may be on Earth, but we're the\Nspace navy. We don't have jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:03:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that this is their turf.\NWe'll simply offer helpful suggestions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say, they picked an interesting\Nspot to come down in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Dorssia's a barren wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We came down out in the boonies, that's all.\NI'm just glad it's not snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our entry angle was just 0.2 degrees off,\Nand we end up way out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for. I can't believe we landed\Nright in the middle of enemy territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal. We're here to pound\Nthe crap out of Dorssia, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like this fool still doesn't understand\Nwhat "force reconnaissance" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What did you say?!\N- Get it into your head already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We landed in the enemy's lap. We got\Nno choice but to fight now, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a one-track mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be \Nfighting among ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we have to think of\N a way to reach JIOR from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder just how far away it is.\NYou got a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... L-elf is thinking of one. Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're turning to him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He's saved our lives on a bunch\Nof occasions up until now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I imagine it? But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There was blood splatter, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith in L-elf. We need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The objective of this operation is\Nto procure a means of transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. We abandoned the shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So where do we get this\Nmeans of transport?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the Dorssian army.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the enemy?! Sure, a military transport\Nwould be able to carry the Valvraves, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yet another tall order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But compared to a consumer product,\Nits performance would be a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound easy,\Nbut how do we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We send spies into the enemy ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This team will be Saki Rukino\N and Akira Renbokoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go outside? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira Renbokoji. We need your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! We can't send Akira-chan in undercover!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would be cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Rukkie, you're... You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're... You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they don't feel\Nprotective about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of skill set, it would\Nbe difficult for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Akira isn't ready to—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tough it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look, I'm happy that you want to do\N this for your big brother, Akira,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but don't push yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this will\Nfool the Dorssians?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cobbling together a bunch of spare parts\Nto look like a Valvrave is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work. L-elf said it just has\Nto put doubt in their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The goal is to buy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sashinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a call from the ARUS\NMinistry of Foreign Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From ARUS? Not Dorssia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They say that the five Valvraves came\Ndown in Dorssian territory, not JIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reply from JIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They want to know where\Ntheir friends came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As we thought, they don't appear to have\Nany means of contacting the Valvraves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although the dimensions and mass of the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvrave spotted at Module 77\N match the Figaro Report,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the probability that it is a fake\Nseems to be quite high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play along and pretend\Nto be fooled by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there are other Valvraves at Module 77,\Nit will probably put pressure on Dorssia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. We'll word it as the government confirming\Na civilian news organization scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a draft prepared right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of 101... The Magius...\NWhat plans are they setting in motion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're really taking her with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much time. We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Through here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've already confirmed that this\Nleads to the surface up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Already confirmed?\NYou know this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I built this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take a close look a the layout, everyone.\NDrill L-elf's plan into your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The bombs go further inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, they don't\Ngo off that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"That easily," he says...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they can be triggered to\Ngo off really easily, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I see what he's doing.\NHe's cautious, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, could you hand me a screwdriver?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I just need a screwdriver...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I didn't expect you\Nto come with us, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I asked L-elf about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said that you volunteered\Nto come to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I thought that if I came\Ndown to Earth, I might remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you were the one who\Nproposed this operation, Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What made you decide to go to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot that I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to the situation in JIOR?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About the Valvraves, about the reason\Nfor this war, and... about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Haru—\N- Tokishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Food's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like they say, an army\Nmarches on its stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People in the past had\Nsome good sayings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's still some\Ncurry-flavored left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure I can have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed that you found\Nthis path, Q-vier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's our runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say, X. Can I shoot him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that out, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Q-vier, permission granted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Permission acknowledged!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Q-vier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of a gunshot would carry\Na long way here. Use a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't encourage him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger! A knife it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You actually pulled a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give me authorization, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... a village?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It hasn't changed\Nat all since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, people actually live\Nin a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The pride of the Dorssian army,\Nthe Ideal Blume mobile base weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It establishes a bridgehead by making\Nassault landings inside enemy lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a revolutionary weapon that made\Nthe Third Blitz War possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what attacked\Nthe JIOR mainland?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I forget, how do you say "Hello?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really hasn't changed, not one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must work for the Karlstein Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two of you? Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Karlstein Agency.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It may look like a typical settlement, but it's actually\Na top-secret facility that trains Dorssian agents.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were told to kill\Nanyone suspicious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill any informants.\NKill any deserters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill any witnesses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine, so don't come out yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... the blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me? I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we didn't kill them,\Nwe would be killed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I explained it back at the Moon, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We Kamitsuki are indestructible.\NWounds heal up in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Almost, give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry. We're proceeding to\Nthe next step right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids, did you kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. We have use for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saki Rukino. Akira Renbokoji. Body-jack these\Ntwo and infiltrate the Dorssian army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's time. I'll go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stick to the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will do. I'll see you on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a record of the\Nmonitor feed in the cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I look at that, I'll know for sure\Nif I was imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marie, right? Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know you. Pino and Marie. Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? But you're—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the real me. What's important is that\Nyou and I are friends. Starting 5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Five years!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Friends! Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your goal is to lure the\Nenemy force to this hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When they arrive at the hill, we collapse the ground\Nbeneath them using the bombs we planted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, we'll knock them down\Ninto that cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira Renbokoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your job is to infiltrate the Dorssian army in all the\Nconfusion and hack the transport ship from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-Th-Tha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From oh-three-hundred last night until the present,\Ndid any of you detect anything out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I observed unusual activity\Non the hill to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two boys, late teens. One girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the language two of them used,\NI believe them to be JIORan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect\Nfrom a Karlstein boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can lead us there, I take it?\NWe'll head for the north hill at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blitzendegen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He took the bait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did one of them have silver hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These two are L-elf's old squadmates!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begging your pardon, sirs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We understand. We'll go strictly\Nin the capacity of observers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the event of an engagement, command\Nauthority rests with you. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He has silver hair and a\Nreal nasty look in his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe he was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad! Maybe they're students, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those questions fall under\Nour purview as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You remember me from 5 years ago?\NYou've met me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! It's Pino!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot? Don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember. My only memories\Nare of the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me. Do you know\Nthe old me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it. It's because\NI ate Runes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ate? Absorbed? Sorry.\NMy speaking is bad again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because they reset system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NWhat are you? You aren't an OS?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This body is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Renbokoji. We're in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Commence operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unit 3, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your objective is to destroy\Nthe Blume. Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger that! I'm gonna\Ndo this with gusto!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's started.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the firepower on that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I fly, my temperature's gonna spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Ideal Blume, the Dorssian army's\Nmost powerful weapon. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They had another one hidden, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Blume's downward fire offers unparalleled power against\Nland combat weapons with thin top armor plating,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but Unit 5 can focus all its\Ndefensive capabilities overhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not stopping?\NI can't believe this thing's defenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's your cue, Familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Ideal Blume. With the arrival of the Valvraves,\Nyou're already a weapon of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! Now Haruto is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, since we're going in turns.\NWait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Haruto next? Did I get it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, Haruto isn't here. L-elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marie. You... were talking with the\NValvrave just now, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I'm—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it. Your right eye was injured\Nduring reentry, and it healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:20:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I saw. When we got\Nto Earth, your eye was healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! You and me were\Nmore than enough for the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fighters? I've never seen that type before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They all look the same\Nafter you shoot 'em down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Output, 20%. Thermal emission values nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phase 3, clear. Proceeding to aircraft\Noperational test phase 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask you one more time.\NHaruto, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not human?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me everything.\NAbout this Valvrave, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When Dorssia came to Module 77, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get into your Valvrave, Haruto Tokishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The battle has already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.55,0:21:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirchbaums, proceeding to\Nannihilation output.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirchbaums, you are cleared to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful! We don't have any intel on these!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Makes no difference to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you shoot Marie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the secret of the Kamitsuki got out, this\Ncombat group would no longer be viable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that! Violence is\Nyour answer for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.28,0:24:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, episode 16,\N"Marie Set Free."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.91,0:24:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvrave the Liberator... The system\Nthat will expose the truth of the world.